    **Robo**: Wir hatten einmal `Set.mem_setOf`, das wird dir helfen!"
    rw [mem_setOf]
    Branch
      -- also possible:
      rw [mem_setOf] at *
    Branch
      -- Note: We delete `ha` and `hb` for the hints, so that the user sees the hints even
